* &quot;Herblock: A Cartoonist&#x27;s Life&quot;. Maxwell Macmillan International, 1993.
* &quot;Herblock at Large: &quot;Let&#x27;s Go Back a Little ...&quot; and Other Cartoons with Commentary&quot; Pantheon Books, 1987.
